# ======================================================
# 根目录 .dockerignore - 排除根目录无关文件
# ======================================================

# 依赖和构建产物
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/target/
**/build/
**/out/
**/.cache/
**/.vite/

# 日志、临时文件、截图和测试产物
**/logs/
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/tmp/
**/temp/
**/screenshots/
**/test-results/
**/playwright-report/
**/coverage/

# IDE / OS / Git
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.iml
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
.git/
.gitignore
.trae/
